TITLE: How Kyrsten Sinema's decision makes Democrats' 2024 Senate map tighter
SUMMARY: Arizona Sen. Kyrsten Sinema decided to shake up the political world on Friday by becoming an independent. Now, instead of 49 Democrats and two independents within their ranks, the caucus has 48 Democrats and three independents.
